Iutarot e Daudi te nchetata e Nkaji e Nkai


1  Eiturrurro apa Daudi te Yerusalem ilkituaak pooki le Israel, ilkituaak loo loshon, o larikok le lelo turrurri apa ooisiaai olaiguanani, o larikok le njore le nkalifu, o larikok le njore le maa iip, o laitashiekinok loo masaa pooki, o nkishu o laiguanani, o layiok lenyena, tenebo o lkituaak le nkaji o laiguanani, o lelo tung'ana magil, o lelo murran pooki yiolot. 
2   Nedumunye Daudi aitashe nejo, “Entoning'oki nanu, ilalashera lainei oltung'ana laainei. Atadamua apa to ltau lai pee ashetu enkaji nairragieki osanduku lo sotua lo Laitoriani, neaku eneitasheyie nkejek e Nkai ang: naitobira nanu mbaa naashetieki, 
3  kake aatiaka nanu Enkai, ‘Mindim iyie atesheta enkaji tenkaraki enkarna ai, amu ira iyie olmurrani nimbukoyie osarge sapuk.' 
4  Ore ake eyia aategelua nanu Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel te nkaji e papaai pooki pee aaku olaiguanani le Israel ntarasi, amu etegelua Yuda metaa olarikoni, naa ore te nkaji e Yuda, teina aji e papa, o tiatua ilayiok le papa neitishipa ninye pee aaitaa olaiguanani le Israel pooki. 
5  Naa ore too layiok laainei pooki (amu aaishoo Olaitoriani ilayiok kumok) netegelua Solomon olayioni lai, pee eton to lorika le nkitoo le nkitoria o Laitoriani te Israel. 
6  Aatiaka ninye nanu, ‘Solomon olayioni lino olo ashet enkaji ai o lgorieti laainei, amu ategelua nanu ninye metaa enkerai ai, naa kaaku nanu menye lenye. 
7  Kaitasheyie nanu enkitoria enye ntarasi tenebik ninye aibung neitabaya nkitanapat aainei, o nkikoot aainei, anaa enatiu ninye taata.’ 
8  Ore naa taata te dukuya Isirael pooki, ena umata o Laitoriani o te ning'oto e Nkai ang, entujurru ning'oruru nkitanapat pooki o Laitoriani Enkai inyi; pee itumutumu aawaita ena kop sidai aaitaa eninyi, ningueikiki nkera inyi metaa enjung'ore enye ntarasi.


9  “Naa ore iyie Solomon enkerai ai, tayiolo Enkai e papaai lino, nisiaai ninye to ltau pooki o te ndamunoto e yieunoto amu kejur Olaitoriani iltauja pooki, neyiolo pooki kitobirat o endamunoto. Tening'oru iyie ninye, naa eitum iyie ninye, kake tenilam ninye, naa eikinturraa ninye iyie ntarasi. 
10  Toning'o naa taata, amu kitegelua iyie Olaitoriani pee ishet enkaji naaku ewueji sinyati; ntagoluoyu taasa ina.”


11  Neisho Daudi Solomon eutaroto enkitobirata eina aji Enkai pooki, o enoo nkajijik enyena, o neeshumishoreki, o lgilat lenyena le shumata, o lgilat lenyena liatua, o lgilat lo lorika lolng'ur, 
12  o nena kitobirat pooki naata to ltau, tenkaraki ilgorieti le nkaji o Laitoriani, o lgilat pooki oomanita, o wuejitin pooki neeshumishoreki e nkaji e Nkai, o eneshumieki nkishorot naaitisinyaki; 
13  tenkaraki lelo turrurri loo lapolosak o Lawi, o esiaai pooki enkisiaayiare tiatua enkaji o Laitoriani, o masaa pooki e nkisiaayiare tiatua enkaji o Laitoriani, 
14  o enkiroishi e sahabu tenkaraki imasaa e sahabu te pooki kisiaayiare, o enkiroishi oo masaa e nkosholai te pooki kisiayiare. 
15  O enkiroishi oo nkitasheta oo ltaai, lenye, o enkiroishi e pooki kitashet oltaa o ltaai lenyena, o enkiroishi enkosholai tenkaraki enkiteshet oltaa, o ltaai lenyena, te risioroto enkisiaayiarete pooki kitashet o ltaa. 
16  O enkiroishi e sahabu te pooki mesa, e mukate e nkitoduaaroto, o enkosholai tenkaraki imisai naaitobiri te nkosholai. 
17  O sahabu nasila naitobirieki nkijikoni oo lala, o mbesenini, o nkikompeni, o nena girran e sahabu, o enkiroishi e sahabu naitobirieki pooki o ngirran e nkosholai. 
18  O te nkaraki olperere lo lasar le nkorropil le sahabu nasila, o enkiroishi e sahabu naitobirieki. Neisho sii nkitobirat tenkaraki engarri oo lbartan e sahabu nanapieki lelo kerubi oolak inaipuko enye aaitoip ilo sanduku lo sotua le Nkai. 
19  Eibalunye ninye kuna baa pooki too lkigerot le nkaina o Laitoriani, ooipirta ena bae. Keasi ena siaai pooki aaiturubare ina kitobirata e utaroto.


20  Neitoki Daudi ajoki Solomon ilo ayioni lenye, “Ntagoluoyu nintagol oshoke, niaas ina, miureishoyu, milepori nimishalu; amu ore Olaitoriani Enkai ai, ee Enkai ai, netii tenebo iyie, mikintiak ninye iyie nimikinguanare ometaba anaa neidipayu esiaai pooki e nkisiaayiare e nkaji Olaitoriani. Naa ng'ura, ore ilturrurri loo lapolosak; o loo Lawi, teina kisiaayiare pooki enkaji e Nkai, netii tenebo iyie, ometaba anaa neidipayu esiaai pooki e nkisiaayiare e nkaji Olaitoriani. 
21  Naa ng'ura, ore ilturrurri loo lapolosak, o loo Lawi, teina kisiaayiare pooki enkaji e Nkai netii tenebo iyie, neeta ake pooki tung'ani eyieunoto, neeta pooki ng'ae enkarriyiano te pooki kisiaayiare; ore sii ilkituaak o ltung'ana pooki naa kening aakurraki tenintanap ninche.”

